lead_paragraph: The Whig journals in Ohio say that the election which comes off in that State in a few days will be one of the most important in its results ever had in that section. It is the first under the new Constitution, and upon the General Assembly now to be elected under this instrument will devolve the duty of revising many existing laws and enacting new ones to meet its requirements.
